raw"}, {"accession": "PRIDE:0000408", "name": "Search engine output file URI", "value": "ftp://ftp.pride.ebi.ac.uk/pride/data/archive/2019/01/PXD011344/C8471FD.msf"}, {"accession": "PRIDE:0000404", "name": "Associated raw file URI", "value": "ftp://ftp.pride.ebi.ac.uk/pride/data/archive/2019/01/PXD011344/C8471FD.raw"}, {"accession": "PRIDE:0000408", "name": "Search engine output file URI", "value": "ftp://ftp.pride.ebi.ac.uk/pride/data/archive/2019/01/PXD011344/C8472FD.msf"}, {"accession": "PRIDE:0000404", "name": "Associated raw file URI", "value": "ftp://ftp.pride.ebi.ac.uk/pride/data/archive/2019/01/PXD011344/C8472FD.raw"}, {"accession": "PRIDE:0000408", "name": "Search engine output file URI", "value": "ftp://ftp.pride.ebi.ac.uk/pride/data/archive/2019/01/PXD011344/C8473FD.msf"}, {"accession": "PRIDE:0000404", "name": "Associated raw file URI", "value": "ftp://ftp.pride.ebi.ac.uk/pride/data/archive/2019/01/PXD011344/C8473FD.raw"}, {"accession": "PRIDE:0000408", "name": "Search engine output file URI", "value": "ftp://ftp.pride.ebi.ac.uk/pride/data/archive/2019/01/PXD011344/C8474FD.msf"}, {"accession": "PRIDE:0000404", "name": "Associated raw file URI", "value": "ftp://ftp.pride.ebi.ac.uk/pride/data/archive/2019/01/PXD011344/C8474FD.raw"}, {"accession": "PRIDE:0000408", "name": "Search engine output file URI", "value": "ftp://ftp.pride.ebi.ac.uk/pride/data/archive/2019/01/PXD011344/C8475FD.msf"}, {"accession": "PRIDE:0000404", "name": "Associated raw file URI", "value": "ftp://ftp.pride.ebi.ac.uk/pride/data/archive/2019/01/PXD011344/C8475FD.raw"}, {"accession": "PRIDE:0000408", "name": "Search engine output file URI", "value": "ftp://ftp.pride.ebi.ac.uk/pride/data/archive/2019/01/PXD011344/C8476FD.msf"}, {"accession": "PRIDE:0000404", "name": "Associated raw file URI", "value": "ftp://ftp.pride.ebi.ac.uk/pride/data/archive/2019/01/PXD011344/C8476FD.raw"}, {"accession": "PRIDE:0000410", "name": "'Other' type file URI", "value": "ftp://ftp.pride.ebi.ac.uk/pride/data/archive/2019/01/PXD011344/design_JZ.xlsx"}], "description": "During development, transcriptional and chromatin modification changes co-occur but the order and causality of events often remain unclear. We explore the interrelationship of these processes using the paradigm of X-chromosome inactivation (XCI). We initiate XCI in female, mouse embryonic stem cells by inducing Xist expression and monitor changes in transcription and chromatin by allele-specific TT-seq and ChIP-seq respectively. An unprecedented temporal resolution enabled identification of the earliest chromatin alterations during XCI. We demonstrate that HDAC3 interacts with both NCOR1 and NCOR2 and is pre-bound on the X chromosome where it deacetylates histones to promote efficient gene silencing. We also reveal the choreography of polycomb accumulation following Xist RNA coating, with PRC1-associated H2AK119Ub preceding PRC2-associated H3K27me3. Furthermore, polycomb-associated marks accumulate initially at large, intergenic domains and then spreads into genes but only in the context of gene silencing. Our results provide the hierarchy of chromatin events during XCI and demonstrate that some chromatin changes play key roles in mediating transcriptional silencing.", "fullDatasetLinks": [{"accession": "PRIDE:0000411", "name": "Dataset FTP location", "value": "ftp://ftp.pride.ebi.ac.uk/pride/data/archive/2019/01/PXD011344"}, {"accession": "MS:1001930", "name": "PRIDE project URI", "value": "http://www.ebi.ac.uk/pride/archive/projects/PXD011344"}], "identifiers": [{"accession": "MS:1001919", "name": "ProteomeXchange accession number", "value": "PXD011344"}], "instruments": [{"accession": "MS:1002416", "name": "Orbitrap Fusion"}], "keywords": [{"accession": "MS:1001925", "name": "submitter keyword", "value": "X chromosome inactivation; mouse embryonic stem cells; epigenomics; transcriptomics; histone deacetylation; Polycomb; histone acetylation"}, {"accession": "MS:1001926", "name": "curator keyword", "value": "Biological"}], "modifications": [{"accession": "PRIDE:0000398", "name": "No PTMs are included in the dataset"}], "publications": [{"terms": [{"accession": "MS:1000879", "name": "PubMed identifier", "value": "30595450"}, {"accession": "PRIDE:0000400", "name": "Reference", "value": "\u017bylicz JJ, Bousard A, \u017dumer K, Dossin F, Mohammad E, da Rocha ST, Schwalb B, Syx L, Dingli F, Loew D, Cramer P, Heard E. The Implication of Early Chromatin Changes in X Chromosome Inactivation. Cell. 2019 176(1-2):182-197.e23"}]}], "species": [{"terms": [{"accession": "MS:1001469", "name": "taxonomy: scientific name", "value": "Mus musculus (Mouse)"}, {"accession": "MS:1001467", "name": "taxonomy: NCBI TaxID", "value": "10090"}]}], "title": "The role of early chromatin changes in X chromosome inactivation"}